{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--TagSeXkZksrR1_R7Y7R6Y--><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/520715de609ad9dc.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-d0d7fc50fd05f285.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/acfafb44-8249079a6627ac92.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/920-f9bfc1b0d0402c3e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-1f031e85fdbd8d99.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/898-dd3a73578fffcbfe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/151-ba81253e12657fd6.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/page-02189c9411577ad4.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>About | Matthew Schuppel</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A clean personal hub for professional presence, life systems, documents, planning, and the resources that keep each week moving.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-sans antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-ink/10 bg-paper/85 backdrop-blur-xl\"><nav class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col gap-4 px-5 py-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-3 text-ink\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-md bg-ink text-sm font-semibold text-paper shadow-crisp\">MS</span><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight transition group-hover:text-moss\">Matthew Schuppel</span></a><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1 text-sm\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 py-2 font-medium text-ink/70 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-ink hover:shadow-sm \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 py-2 font-medium text-ink/70 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-ink hover:shadow-sm \" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 py-2 font-medium text-ink/70 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-ink hover:shadow-sm \" href=\"/resume\">Resume</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 py-2 font-medium text-ink/70 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-ink hover:shadow-sm \" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 py-2 font-medium text-ink/70 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-ink hover:shadow-sm border border-ink/10 bg-white/70 text-ink\" href=\"/dashboard\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock-keyhole\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"16\" r=\"1\"></circle><rect x=\"3\" y=\"10\" width=\"18\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 10V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3\"></path></svg>Dashboard</a></div></nav></header><main class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><section class=\"border-b border-ink/10 bg-white/45\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-12 sm:py-16\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-clay\">About</p><h1 class=\"mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-6xl\">A practical, systems-minded overview.</h1></div></section><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-10 sm:py-14\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]\"><aside class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-ink\">Currently</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-ink/70\">Open to selected collaborations and advisory conversations.</p><div class=\"mt-6 border-t border-ink/10 pt-6 text-sm text-ink/65\"><p>Madison, Wisconsin</p><p>hello@example.com</p></div></aside><div class=\"space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/72\"><p>This site is built to be both a professional front door and a personal command center. The public side keeps the essentials easy to find. The private side gives everyday planning a calmer, more durable place to live.</p><p>Replace this copy with your story: the kind of work you do, the problems you like, the values you bring into teams, and the personal context you want people to understand.</p><p>The structure is intentionally simple so it can grow with you: add case studies, writing, embedded documents, or deeper dashboard integrations over time.</p></div></div><section class=\"mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Clear direction</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">Turn vague goals into visible next steps, owners, dates, and decision points.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Useful systems</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">Build lightweight structures that make repeated work easier without adding ceremony.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-list-checks text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m3 17 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"m3 7 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M13 6h8\"></path><path d=\"M13 12h8\"></path><path d=\"M13 18h8\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Reliable follow-through</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">Keep details organized so teams, households, and projects can keep momentum.</p></article></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"border-t border-ink/10 bg-ink text-paper\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-10 text-sm sm:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] sm:items-end\"><div><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Matthew Schuppel</p><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-xl text-paper/65\">A clean personal hub for professional presence, life systems, documents, planning, and the resources that keep each week moving.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2 text-paper/70 sm:text-right\"><p>yourdomain.com</p><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> All rights reserved.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-d0d7fc50fd05f285.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[8898,[\\\"898\\\",\\\"static/chunks/898-dd3a73578fffcbfe.js\\\",\\\"151\\\",\\\"static/chunks/1